:

1. *Tajni* agent je morao da se preruši u turistu da bi prošao neopažen. (The secret agent had to disguise himself as a tourist in order to pass unnoticed.)

2. Ona je imala *tajni* dnevnik u kome je sakrivala svoje misli. (She had a secret diary where she kept her thoughts.)

3. U njegovom životu postoje mnogi *tajni* koje ne znamo. (There are many secrets in his life that we don't know.)

4. On se učlanio u *tajni* klub čiji su članovi bili isključivo bogati. (He joined a secret club whose members were exclusively wealthy.)

5. On je izdao *tajni* dokument koji je dovelo do nesporazuma. (He leaked a secret document that caused misunderstanding.)